== 利用狀況 ==
截至2013年12月，跑華街站是灣區捷運系統中最繁忙的車站<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bart.gov/about/reports/ridership |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-10-16 |archive-date=2016-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107071934/http://www.bart.gov/about/reports/ridership |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2015年則是第三繁忙的車站（前两名分别是{{站|内河码头}}和{{站|蒙哥马利街}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/place/article/Sunken-Hallidie-Plaza-was-a-deeply-wrong-design-6626025.php?t=e0253ef4b13e72cb18|title = Sunken Hallidie Plaza was a deeply wrong design idea|last = King|first = John|date = 2015-11-11|website = San Francisco Chronicle|access-date = 2016-04-11|archive-date = 2016-04-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422181213/http://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/place/article/Sunken-Hallidie-Plaza-was-a-deeply-wrong-design-6626025.php?t=e0253ef4b13e72cb18|dead-url = no}}</ref>。本站的主要使用者為遊客、購物者，但也有[[露宿者|露宿者]]及[[街头艺人|街头艺人]]等在本站逗留。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://oversea.stnn.cc/SF/2014/1223/166243.shtml|title=湾区捷运各站 跑华街站最不太平|publisher=[[星島日報|星島日報]]三藩分社|date=2014-12-23|accessdate=2016-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018201531/http://oversea.stnn.cc/SF/2014/1223/166243.shtml|archive-date=2016-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在本站及市區內的其他車站，部分乘客在晚高峰不得不反向乘車至{{站|葛连公园}}等客流較低的車站，以避開跨灣的大客流。<ref name=crush>{{cite news|url=http://m.sfgate.com/bpm_test/article/BART-can-t-keep-pace-with-rising-crush-loads-6234574.php|title=BART can’t keep pace with rising 'crush loads’|work=SFGate|date=April 10, 2010|first=Michael|last=Cabanatuan|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611093549/http://m.sfgate.com/bpm_test/article/BART-can-t-keep-pace-with-rising-crush-loads-6234574.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

